# Contributor License Agreement

This Contributor License Agreement ("Agreement") is agreed to by the party signing below ("You"), and conveys certain license rights to Your contributions to Science Communications World Wide e.V for the World-Wide.org project. This Agreement is effective as of the date You first submitted a Contribution to us. Co-founders of Science Communications World Wide e.V are Panos Bozelos and Tim Vogels.

## 1. Definitions

"Contribution" shall mean any original work of authorship, including any modifications or additions to an existing work, that is submitted by You to us for inclusion in, or documentation of, the World-Wide.org project.

"We" or "Us" shall mean the Science Communications World Wide e.V, the owner(s) of the World-Wide.org project.

